/PG338/XX/PR

This is our God./PR

This is our source./PR

This is our sovereign./PR

This is our saving power./PR

And this one, mercifully,/PR

shall declare a second time,/PR

for every living being to hear,/PR

confirming Godòs divinity for you:/PR

"I am the /SCO/XXMNIPRESENT /XXO/XXNE/XX, your God!"/PR

/PR

O, mighty one, our mighty one,/PR

/SCT/XXHE /XXS/XXOVEREIGN/XX who watches over us,/PR

how mighty is your name throughout the earth!/PR

The time shall come that /SCG/XXOD/XX will reign/PR

throughout the earth. On that day/PR

shall /SCT/XXHE /XXF/XXOUNT OF /XXL/XXIFE/XX be one,/PR

the divine name be one./PR

And as is written in your sacred words of psalm:/PR

"May /SCT/XXHE /XXE/XXTERNAL/XX reign forever,/PR

your God, O Zion, from one generation to the next. Halleluyah!"/PR

/PR

From one generation to the next/PR

may we declare your greatness,/PR

and for all eternities may we affirm your holiness,/PR

And may your praise, our God,/PR

never be absent from our mouths/PR

now and forever./PR

For you are a great and holy God./PR

Blessed are you, /SCT/XXHE /XXA/XXWESOME /XXO/XXNE/XX, the holy God./PI/PR

םכיהלא...ינא / I...God! (Numbers 15:41)./PR

